A young man was mown down and shot by a gang in Glasgow.The 29-year-old was hit by a white 4x4 car in Royston Road at around 6.30pm on Thursday.When he was on the ground, the victim was shot by an occupant of the vehicle.He was rushed to hospital and is currently detained in a serious but stable condition.The Evening Times understands the incident was gang related.Police said the white 4x4 Mitsubishi vehicle was later found dumped in Royston.